---
import DemoLayout from '../../../layouts/DemoLayout.astro';
---

<DemoLayout
  title="Waiting Room Demo"
  description="Explore how Cloudflare manages surges in website traffic with virtual waiting rooms."
  category="Application Performance"
  labels={["Waiting Room"]}
  lastUpdated="March 2025"
>

  <!-- Overview Card -->
  <section class="card" aria-labelledby="overview-heading">
    <h2 id="overview-heading">Overview</h2>
    <p>
      Explore how Cloudflare manages surges in website traffic with virtual waiting rooms and different{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/waiting-room/reference/queueing-methods/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
        queueing methods
      </a>.
    </p>

    <p>There are several relevant features:</p>
    <ul class="feature-list">
      <li>
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/waiting-room/how-to/customize-waiting-room/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          <strong>Customize the Waiting Room design</strong>
        </a>, which also supports{' '}
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/waiting-room/how-to/customize-waiting-room/#multiple-language-support" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          multiple-languages
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/waiting-room/reference/best-practices/#waiting-room-and-seo" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          <strong>Enable SEO Crawler Bypassing</strong>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/waiting-room/additional-options/create-events/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          <strong>Schedule events</strong>
        </a>
      </li>
      <li>
        <a href="https://blog.cloudflare.com/banish-bots-from-your-waiting-room-and-improve-wait-times-for-real-users/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
          <strong>Send bots to an infinite queue</strong>
        </a>
      </li>
    </ul>

    <p class="mt-1">
      This solution is part of the{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/fundamentals/performance/preparing-for-surges-or-spikes-in-web-traffic/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
        preparing for surges or spikes in web traffic
      </a>
      {' '}guide, especially useful during seasonal events, such as Black Friday or Christmas.
    </p>

    <p class="mt-1">
      After an event ends, the{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/waiting-room/reference/queueing-methods/#reject" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
        <strong>reject</strong>
      </a>
      {' '}queueing method can be used to block traffic from reaching the application, displaying a custom HTML
      template instead. This template can also be{' '}
      <a href="https://developers.cloudflare.com/api/resources/waiting_rooms/methods/edit/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer external">
        <strong>updated or patched</strong>
      </a>
      {' '}to signal that the event is over.
    </p>

    <div class="btn-row mt-1">
      <a
        href="https://performance.cf-testing.com/cloudflare-waiting-room-demo.html"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer external"
        class="btn btn-secondary"
      >
        Visit Demo
      </a>
      <a
        href="https://gist.github.com/DavidJKTofan/43b0ef91269a3389b51cad578b1b7d90"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer external"
        class="btn btn-secondary"
      >
        Custom HTML Template
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Waiting Room Settings Screenshot -->
  <section aria-labelledby="settings-heading">
    <h2 id="settings-heading">Waiting Room Settings</h2>
    <div class="img-container">
      <img
        src="/demos/performance/img/cf-zone-waiting-room.png"
        alt="Cloudflare Zone Waiting Room Dashboard Settings"
        loading="lazy"
      />
    </div>
  </section>

</DemoLayout>

<style>
  /* ===== Section spacing ===== */
  section {
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  section > h2 {
    font-size: clamp(1.15rem, 3vw, 1.45rem);
    color: var(--secondary);
    margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
    padding-bottom: 0.5rem;
    border-bottom: 2px solid var(--border);
  }

  /* ===== Card ===== */
  .card {
    background-color: var(--card);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 10px;
    padding: 1.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
  }

  .card h2 {
    border-bottom-color: var(--border);
  }

  .card p, section > p {
    margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== Feature list ===== */
  .feature-list {
    list-style: disc;
    padding-left: 1.5rem;
    margin: 0.75rem 0 1rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.4rem;
    line-height: 1.7;
  }

  /* ===== Utility ===== */
  .mt-1 { margin-top: 1rem; }

  /* ===== Button Row ===== */
  .btn-row {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 0.75rem;
  }

  .btn {
    display: inline-block;
    padding: 0.6rem 1.2rem;
    border-radius: 6px;
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    text-decoration: none;
    border: none;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: opacity 0.2s, transform 0.15s;
    border-bottom: none !important;
    min-width: 180px;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .btn:hover {
    opacity: 0.9;
    transform: translateY(-1px);
    border-bottom: none !important;
  }

  .btn-secondary {
    background-color: var(--secondary);
    color: white;
  }

  /* ===== Image Container ===== */
  .img-container {
    border-radius: 8px;
    overflow: hidden;
    border: 2px solid var(--secondary);
  }

  .img-container img {
    width: 100%;
    height: auto;
    display: block;
  }

  /* ===== Mobile ===== */
  @media (max-width: 600px) {
    .btn-row { flex-direction: column; }
    .btn { min-width: unset; }
  }
</style>
